                                <title>Mästägabǝ’, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መስተጋብዕ፡</foreign></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ወለቡ፡ ጽራኅየ፡ ወአጽምአኒ፡ ቃለ፡ ስእለትየ፡ ከመ፡ ወልታ፡ ሥሙር፡ ከለልከነ፡ እግዚኦ፡ እግዚኦ፡ በመዓትከ፡ ኢትቅሥፈኒ፡ ወበመቅሰፍትከ፡ ኢትገሥጸኒ፡</incipit>
                             </msItem>
                             <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                                <locus from="26v" to="32r" facs="029">Fols 26v–32r</locus>
                                <title>Qalǝyä aṣmǝ`, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቃልየ፡ አጽምዕ፡</foreign></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ቃልየ፡ አጽምእ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወለቡ፡ ጽራኅየ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወአጽምአኒ፡ ቃለ፡ ስእለትየ፡ ንጉሥየኒ፡ ወአምላኪየኒ፡</incipit>
                             </msItem>
                             <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4">
                                <locus from="32r" to="38r" facs="034">Fols 32r–38r</locus>
                                <title>Aryam, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አርያም፡</foreign></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ለአብ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ለወልድ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ውለመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ቀዳሚ፡ ዜማ፡ ግበሩ፡ በዓለ፡ (በዓለ፡) በትፍሥሕት፡ እስከ፡ አቅርቲሁ፡ ለምሥዋዕ፡</incipit>
                             </msItem>
                             <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5">
                                <locus from="38r" to="49r" facs="040">Fols 38r–49r</locus>
                                <title>Sǝmǝ‘ani, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ስምዓኒ፡</foreign></title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">ስምዓኒ፡ እግዚኦ፡ ጸሎትየ፡ ሃሌ፡ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ወይብጻሕ፡ ቅድሜከ፡ ገዓርየ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/>
                                </incipit>
                             </msItem>
                             <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6">
                                <locus from="49r" to="52r" facs="051">Fols 49r–52r</locus>
                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3178Deggwa#Haleta">Dǝggʷā, Table of
                                                  melodic variations for the Hallelujah (same as
                                                  https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1110Anqasa)</title>
                             </msItem>
                             <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.7">
                                <locus from="52v" to="54r" facs="055">Fols 52v–54r</locus>
                                <title>Sǝmǝ‘ani, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ስምዓኒ፡</foreign></title>
                                <note>supplements, incomplete at the end</note>
